==Savage and Aspies==
[[Image:Savageonkids.jpg|thumb|right|Savage's book on how to [[Rape|properly treat your kids]]]].
Savage has also aroused the ire of the [[Asperger's Syndrome|aspie]] community, causing an immense amount of [[butthurt]] on [[Internet|the Internets]]. [[Last Thursday]], Savage [[LOL WUT|made the claim that kids with autism and their parents were part of a vast liberal conspiracy to collect welfare checks from the Government.]] This is because Savage not only hates [[retards|kids with autism]], but he hates [[poor]] people as well. All this stems from the fact that Michael is in fact a [[retarded]] Shylock growing up a poor Jew raped every night by his ugly swine father. Like most [[retard|well-meaning people]], Savage asserted that the following comments were taken [[lie|out of context]], by [[Jews|liberals]] seeking to have Savage's show removed from the airwaves:

{{quote|Now, the illness du jour is [[autism]]. You know what autism is? I'll tell you what autism is. In 99 percent of the cases, it's a brat who hasn't been told to cut the act out. That's what autism is.|Dr. Savage's [[irony|educated assertion of autism and its effects on behavior in children]]}}

{{quote|What do you mean they scream and they're silent? They don't have a father around to tell them, "Don't act like a moron. You'll get nowhere in life. Stop acting like a Jew. Straighten up. Act like a man. Don't sit there crying and screaming, idiot.|Michael Savage, being a fucking [[douchebag]]}}

[[Butthurt]] ensued. Within days of [[last Thursday]], as [[TOW]] reports, a steady stream of parents and grandparents of [[retards]] lined up at Savage's New York radio studio, and angrily [[masturbation|protested]]. Companies that once sponsored the airtime that Savage's show worked on quickly withdrew support, and Savage decided to dedicate his next show to [[BAWWW|confronting offended parents]]. This, of course made [[for great justice]] on the part of some parents who had been [[offended|seriously offended]] by Savage's [[santorum|santorum-coated]] comments:

{{quote|I can tell you who is a brat. That would be Michael Savage, not the autistic people of Montana.| Brian Schweitzer, governor of [[Brokeback Mountain|The Great State of Montana]] and father of a [[retard]], epitomizing [[NO U]]}}

Several [[rich and beautiful]] celebrity parents of [[autism|asspies]] issued statements filled with [[BAWWW]], most notably the black person and [[Jenny McCarthy|the dumb bimbo who married Jim Carrey]]. 

{{quote|We find it shocking that the individuals who name-call and pass judgment on families like ours have had zero experience with the disorder|[http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/25804382/ Holly Robinson-Peete and Rodney Peete], a.k.a. [[BAWWW|Mr. and Mrs. BAWWW]]}}

Savage, meanwhile, has retreated to the safe haven of his beloved [[blog]], where to the [[anti-lulz|frunz]] of his [[Republican]] [[fanboys]] who would give all of their precious Social Security money to have one drop of precum from his enormous [[e-penis]], he made a [[lolcow|half-hearted apology.]] As Michael Savage is a [[lolcow]] of the first order, he also has been prone to ''foot-in-mouth'' disease, [[Glenn Beck|which has been known to afflict other old media commentators as well]]. This was evidenced by an assertive [[NO U]] comment on the aforementioned [[blog]]:

{{quote|My comments about autism were meant to boldly awaken parents and children to the medical community’s attempt to label too many children or adults as ‘autistic.’|Michael Savage, failing miserably, lol}}

Savage's production company, [[fail|in their half-assed attempt to save advertising dollars]], set up a [http://www.savageonautism.com/ webpage] containing [[over 9000]] audio comments from Savage's show on [[autism]]. This webpage also contains a defensive [[TL;DR]] statement by Savage's production company in an attempt at [[fail|clarification]]. Nonetheless, the [[over 9000]] clips on the webpage not only outline Savage's views on [[autism|asspies]], but also expose Savage's [[douchebag|extreme douchebaggery]] at attempting to even seem slightly compassionate about the subject of [[autism]]. If there is anything to be learned of this situation, it is that Michael Savage must be [[raped|brutally raped]] [[for great justice]], so that people like [[Chris-chan]] can finally be left to their own [[asspie]] freedoms, saving us from having to deal with their [[furry]] tendencies later in life. 

